in hml on retry — green is offline, refusing to submit on prod`,\n221\t        submit_retry_used: true,\n222\t        marker: null,\n223\t      };\n224\t    }\n225\t    result = await submit(marker);\n226\t    result.retry = true;\n227\t  }\n228\t\n229\t  return {\n230\t    submit_ok: result.ok,\n231\t    submit_reason: result.reason || null,\n232\t    submit_message: result.message || null,\n233\t    submit_retry_used: !!result.retry,\n234\t    marker,\n235\t  };\n236\t}\n237\t```\n238\t\n239\t## Apresentar matriz"}]},"uuid":"c3da6419-644a-4858-939d-64b2cca0408e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:27:58.200Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/.claude/commands/smoke.md","content":"        );\n        if (success) return { ok: true,  message: success.innerText.trim().slice(0, 200) };\n        if (error)   return { ok: false, reason: 'error_message', message: error.innerText.trim().slice(0, 200) };\n        await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 250));\n      }\n      return { ok: false, reason: 'timeout_15s' };\n    }, m);\n  };\n\n  // 1ª checagem: estamos mesmo no green?\n  let guard = await checkGreenLive();\n  if (!guard.is_green) {\n    // Retry 1x com backoff: green ALB rule pode ter sido recém-aplicada\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n    await page.reload({ waitUntil: 'networkidle' });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n    guard = await checkGreenLive();\n    if (!guard.is_green) {\n      return {\n        submit_ok: false,\n        submit_reason: 'green_offline',\n        submit_message: `hostname \"${guard.hostname}\" does not contain hml — green is offline, refusing to submit on prod`,\n        submit_retry_used: true,\n        marker: null,\n      };\n    }\n  }\n\n  let result = await submit(marker);\n\n  if (!result.ok) {\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n    await page.reload({ waitUntil: 'networkidle' });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n    // Re-validar guard de hostname antes da 2ª tentativa (green pode ter caído entre tentativas)\n    const guard2 = await checkGreenLive();\n    if (!guard2.is_green) {\n      return {\n        submit_ok: false,\n        submit_reason: 'green_offline',\n        submit_message: `hostname \"${guard2.hostname}\" does not contain hml on retry — green is offline, refusing to submit on prod`,\n        submit_retry_used: true,\n        marker: null,\n      };\n    }\n    result = await submit(marker);\n    result.retry = true;\n  }\n\n  return {\n    submit_ok: result.ok,\n    submit_reason: result.reason || null,\n    submit_message: result.message || null,\n    submit_retry_used: !!result.retry,\n    marker,\n  };\n}\n```\n\n## Apresentar matriz","numLines":60,"startLine":180,"totalLines":451}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"007538d6-95e2-4f77-ad69-2e02f8237bb5","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"c3da6419-644a-4858-939d-64b2cca0408e","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01DFNMHVbESi1MzGrzVgABR4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01LKj2rYRpYofu1Nc4SZJUxo","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/.claude/commands/smoke.md","offset":238,"limit":60},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1093,"cache_read_input_tokens":641044,"output_tokens":154,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1093,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":154,"cache_read_input_tokens":641044,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1093,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1093},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cacse87dp6YLnUqaUBmZH","type":"assistant","uuid":"e012bc5a-dbaf-488f-8185-395428f0cce3","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:28:04.030Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"e012bc5a-dbaf-488f-8185-395428f0cce3","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"64bea18c-a7d1-4936-a480-de15c47fa18a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LKj2rYRpYofu1Nc4SZJUxo","type":"tool_result","content":"238\t\n239\t## Apresentar matriz\n240\t\n241\t### Páginas 1-5 (conteúdo)\n242\t\n243\t```\n244\t| Página      | PROD hostname | PROD items | PROD jet_max | GREEN hostname | GREEN items | GREEN jet_max | Status |\n245\t|-------------|---------------|-----------:|-------------:|----------------|------------:|--------------:|--------|\n246\t| Home        | blue          |        N   |          N   | hml            |         N   |          N    | ✅     |\n247\t| Atlas PT    | blue          |        1   |          1   | hml            |         4   |        656    | ✅     |\n248\t| Atlas EN    | blue          |        1   |          1   | hml            |         4   |        656    | ✅     |\n249\t| Espiral     | blue          |       12   |         12   | hml            |        12   |         12    | ✅     |\n250\t| Eventos     | blue          |        N   |          N   | hml            |         N   |          N    | ✅     |\n251\t```\n252\t\n253\t### Páginas 6-7 (formulários)\n254\t\n255\t```\n256\t| Página              | PROD form | PROD fields | PROD submit | GREEN submit_ok | retry | marker email                    | Status |\n257\t|---------------------|----------:|------------:|-------------|-----------------|-------|---------------------------------|--------|\n258\t| Newsletter (home)   |     1     |     2       | \"ENVIAR\"    | ✅              | no    | smoke+1730487123@bureau-it.com  | ✅     |\n259\t| Contato             |     1     |     N       | \"ENVIAR\"    | ✅              | yes   | smoke+1730487145@bureau-it.com  | ✅     |\n260\t```\n261\t\n262\tPROD valida apenas presença/campos/label do submit. GREEN executa submit real com marcador rastreável (`smoke+<ts>@bureau-it.com`) e valida resposta visual de sucesso/erro.\n263\t\n264\t## Fase 7.5 — Paridade prod/dev de páginas críticas\n265\t\n266\tCompara renderização da MESMA página em PROD (`concertacaoamazonia.com.br`) e DEV (`concertacao.bureau-it.com` via tunnel). Detecta divergências de DOM/heading/imagens/altura que indicam regressão de deploy mesmo quando HTML retornado parece idêntico.\n267\t\n268\t**Páginas auditadas:** atualmente apenas `/agenda-integradora/`. Adicionar outras quando aparecerem regressões similares.\n269\t\n270\t### Snippet — Paridade prod/dev (rodar 1x por página)\n271\t\n272\t```js\n273\tasync (page) => {\n274\t  const path = '/agenda-integradora/';\n275\t  const prodUrl = 'https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br' + path;\n276\t  const devUrl  = 'https://concertacao.bureau-it.com' + path;\n277\t\n278\t  const measurePage = async (url) => {\n279\t    await page.context().clearCookies();\n280\t    await page.goto(url + '?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 45000 });\n281\t    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n282\t\n283\t    return await page.evaluate(() => {\n284\t      const headings = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3'))\n285\t        .map(h => h.innerText.trim().slice(0, 80))\n286\t        .filter(Boolean);\n287\t      const downloadBtns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, button'))\n288\t        .filter(b => /download/i.test(b.innerText || ''))\n289\t        .map(b => b.innerText.trim().slice(0, 40));\n290\t      const imgsRendered = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('img'))\n291\t        .filter(i => i.naturalWidth >= 100).length;\n292\t\n293\t      return {\n294\t        page_height: document.body.scrollHeight,\n295\t        headings,\n296\t        heading_count: headings.length,\n297\t        download_btns: downloadBtns,"}]},"uuid":"84cdfff6-0f07-4c17-8a99-12b27067f24d","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:28:04.052Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/.claude/commands/smoke.md","content":"\n## Apresentar matriz\n\n### Páginas 1-5 (conteúdo)\n\n```\n| Página      | PROD hostname | PROD items | PROD jet_max | GREEN hostname | GREEN items | GREEN jet_max | Status |\n|-------------|---------------|-----------:|-------------:|----------------|------------:|--------------:|--------|\n| Home        | blue          |        N   |          N   | hml            |         N   |          N    | ✅     |\n| Atlas PT    | blue          |        1   |          1   | hml            |         4   |        656    | ✅     |\n| Atlas EN    | blue          |        1   |          1   | hml            |         4   |        656    | ✅     |\n| Espiral     | blue          |       12   |         12   | hml            |        12   |         12    | ✅     |\n| Eventos     | blue          |        N   |          N   | hml            |         N   |          N    | ✅     |\n```\n\n### Páginas 6-7 (formulários)\n\n```\n| Página              | PROD form | PROD fields | PROD submit | GREEN submit_ok | retry | marker email                    | Status |\n|---------------------|----------:|------------:|-------------|-----------------|-------|---------------------------------|--------|\n| Newsletter (home)   |     1     |     2       | \"ENVIAR\"    | ✅              | no    | smoke+1730487123@bureau-it.com  | ✅     |\n| Contato             |     1     |     N       | \"ENVIAR\"    | ✅              | yes   | smoke+1730487145@bureau-it.com  | ✅     |\n```\n\nPROD valida apenas presença/campos/label do submit. GREEN executa submit real com marcador rastreável (`smoke+<ts>@bureau-it.com`) e valida resposta visual de sucesso/erro.\n\n## Fase 7.5 — Paridade prod/dev de páginas críticas\n\nCompara renderização da MESMA página em PROD (`concertacaoamazonia.com.br`) e DEV (`concertacao.bureau-it.com` via tunnel). Detecta divergências de DOM/heading/imagens/altura que indicam regressão de deploy mesmo quando HTML retornado parece idêntico.\n\n**Páginas auditadas:** atualmente apenas `/agenda-integradora/`. Adicionar outras quando aparecerem regressões similares.\n\n### Snippet — Paridade prod/dev (rodar 1x por página)\n\n```js\nasync (page) => {\n  const path = '/agenda-integradora/';\n  const prodUrl = 'https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br' + path;\n  const devUrl  = 'https://concertacao.bureau-it.com' + path;\n\n  const measurePage = async (url) => {\n    await page.context().clearCookies();\n    await page.goto(url + '?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 45000 });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    return await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const headings = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3'))\n        .map(h => h.innerText.trim().slice(0, 80))\n        .filter(Boolean);\n      const downloadBtns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, button'))\n        .filter(b => /download/i.test(b.innerText || ''))\n        .map(b => b.innerText.trim().slice(0, 40));\n      const imgsRendered = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('img'))\n        .filter(i => i.naturalWidth >= 100).length;\n\n      return {\n        page_height: document.body.scrollHeight,\n        headings,\n        heading_count: headings.length,\n        download_btns: downloadBtns,","numLines":60,"startLine":238,"totalLines":451}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"e012bc5a-dbaf-488f-8185-395428f0cce3","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
