{"parentUuid":"f39565db-840a-4d76-bcad-92ffdf45e513","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"64bea18c-a7d1-4936-a480-de15c47fa18a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Y3gj2kQcMNEj5gQVgVGCyx","type":"tool_result","content":"260\t```\n261\t\n262\tPROD valida apenas presença/campos/label do submit. GREEN executa submit real com marcador rastreável (`smoke+<ts>@bureau-it.com`) e valida resposta visual de sucesso/erro.\n263\t\n264\t## Fase 7.5 — Paridade prod/dev de páginas críticas\n265\t\n266\tCompara renderização da MESMA página em PROD (`concertacaoamazonia.com.br`) e DEV (`concertacao.bureau-it.com` via tunnel). Detecta divergências de DOM/heading/imagens/altura que indicam regressão de deploy mesmo quando HTML retornado parece idêntico.\n267\t\n268\t**Páginas auditadas:** atualmente apenas `/agenda-integradora/`. Adicionar outras quando aparecerem regressões similares.\n269\t\n270\t### Snippet — Paridade prod/dev (rodar 1x por página)\n271\t\n272\t```js\n273\tasync (page) => {\n274\t  const path = '/agenda-integradora/';\n275\t  const prodUrl = 'https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br' + path;\n276\t  const devUrl  = 'https://concertacao.bureau-it.com' + path;\n277\t\n278\t  const measurePage = async (url) => {\n279\t    await page.context().clearCookies();\n280\t    await page.goto(url + '?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 45000 });\n281\t    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n282\t\n283\t    return await page.evaluate(() => {\n284\t      const headings = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3'))\n285\t        .map(h => h.innerText.trim().slice(0, 80))\n286\t        .filter(Boolean);\n287\t      const downloadBtns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, button'))\n288\t        .filter(b => /download/i.test(b.innerText || ''))\n289\t        .map(b => b.innerText.trim().slice(0, 40));\n290\t      const imgsRendered = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('img'))\n291\t        .filter(i => i.naturalWidth >= 100).length;\n292\t\n293\t      return {\n294\t        page_height: document.body.scrollHeight,\n295\t        headings,\n296\t        heading_count: headings.length,\n297\t        download_btns: downloadBtns,\n298\t        download_btn_count: downloadBtns.length,\n299\t        rendered_images: imgsRendered,\n300\t        elementor_sections: document.querySelectorAll('.elementor-section, .e-con').length,\n301\t      };\n302\t    });\n303\t  };\n304\t\n305\t  const prod = await measurePage(prodUrl);\n306\t  const dev  = await measurePage(devUrl);\n307\t\n308\t  // Calcular diffs\n309\t  const headingsMatch = JSON.stringify(prod.headings) === JSON.stringify(dev.headings);\n310\t  const downloadsMatch = JSON.stringify(prod.download_btns) === JSON.stringify(dev.download_btns);\n311\t  const heightDiffPct = Math.abs(prod.page_height - dev.page_height) / Math.max(prod.page_height, dev.page_height);\n312\t  const imagesDiffPct = Math.abs(prod.rendered_images - dev.rendered_images) / Math.max(prod.rendered_images, dev.rendered_images, 1);\n313\t\n314\t  return {\n315\t    page: path,\n316\t    prod, dev,\n317\t    diff: {\n318\t      headings_match: headingsMatch,\n319\t      downloads_match: downloadsMatch,\n320\t      page_height_diff_pct: Math.round(heightDiffPct * 100),\n321\t      rendered_images_diff_pct: Math.round(imagesDiffPct * 100),\n322\t      sections_diff: prod.elementor_sections - dev.elementor_sections,\n323\t    },\n324\t  };\n325\t}\n326\t```\n327\t\n328\t### Apresentar matriz de paridade\n329\t\n330\t```\n331\t| Página              | PROD height | DEV height | Δ% | PROD H | DEV H | H match | PROD btns | DEV btns | Btns match | Status |\n332\t|---------------------|------------:|-----------:|----|-------:|------:|---------|----------:|---------:|------------|--------|\n333\t| /agenda-integradora |    8420     |    8520    | 1% |    7   |   7   | ✅      |     7     |    7     | ✅         | ✅     |\n334\t```\n335\t\n336\t## Fase 8 — Warm-up de cache do menu (prod e green)\n337\t\n338\tDescobre as páginas do menu principal scrappeando a home, faz 2 visitas em sequência (1ª aquece, 2ª mede), e valida que cada item está sendo servido rápido a partir do cache.\n339\t\n340\t### Snippet — Warm-up do menu (rodar 1x para PROD, 1x para GREEN)\n341\t\n342\t```js\n343\tasync (page) => {\n344\t  const ctx = page.context();\n345\t  const isGreen = HEADER_VAL && HEADER_VAL['X-Test-Green'] === 'true';\n346\t  await ctx.setExtraHTTPHeaders(HEADER_VAL || {});\n347\t  await ctx.clearCookies();\n348\t\n349\t  // 1) Descobrir itens do menu na home\n350\t  await page.goto('https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br/?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n351\t  const menuUrls = await page.evaluate(() => {\n352\t    const origin = location.origin;\n353\t    // Cobrir Elementor nav-menu, header padrão WordPress, e <nav> genérico no header\n354\t    const sels = [\n355\t      'header nav a[href]',\n356\t      '.elementor-nav-menu a[href]',\n357\t      '#site-navigation a[href]',\n358\t      '.main-navigation a[href]',\n359\t      'nav.elementor-nav-menu--main a[href]',"}]},"uuid":"03390ce7-7254-46d3-b758-6459d17bd96a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:28:12.605Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/.claude/commands/smoke.md","content":"```\n\nPROD valida apenas presença/campos/label do submit. GREEN executa submit real com marcador rastreável (`smoke+<ts>@bureau-it.com`) e valida resposta visual de sucesso/erro.\n\n## Fase 7.5 — Paridade prod/dev de páginas críticas\n\nCompara renderização da MESMA página em PROD (`concertacaoamazonia.com.br`) e DEV (`concertacao.bureau-it.com` via tunnel). Detecta divergências de DOM/heading/imagens/altura que indicam regressão de deploy mesmo quando HTML retornado parece idêntico.\n\n**Páginas auditadas:** atualmente apenas `/agenda-integradora/`. Adicionar outras quando aparecerem regressões similares.\n\n### Snippet — Paridade prod/dev (rodar 1x por página)\n\n```js\nasync (page) => {\n  const path = '/agenda-integradora/';\n  const prodUrl = 'https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br' + path;\n  const devUrl  = 'https://concertacao.bureau-it.com' + path;\n\n  const measurePage = async (url) => {\n    await page.context().clearCookies();\n    await page.goto(url + '?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 45000 });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    return await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const headings = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3'))\n        .map(h => h.innerText.trim().slice(0, 80))\n        .filter(Boolean);\n      const downloadBtns = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, button'))\n        .filter(b => /download/i.test(b.innerText || ''))\n        .map(b => b.innerText.trim().slice(0, 40));\n      const imgsRendered = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('img'))\n        .filter(i => i.naturalWidth >= 100).length;\n\n      return {\n        page_height: document.body.scrollHeight,\n        headings,\n        heading_count: headings.length,\n        download_btns: downloadBtns,\n        download_btn_count: downloadBtns.length,\n        rendered_images: imgsRendered,\n        elementor_sections: document.querySelectorAll('.elementor-section, .e-con').length,\n      };\n    });\n  };\n\n  const prod = await measurePage(prodUrl);\n  const dev  = await measurePage(devUrl);\n\n  // Calcular diffs\n  const headingsMatch = JSON.stringify(prod.headings) === JSON.stringify(dev.headings);\n  const downloadsMatch = JSON.stringify(prod.download_btns) === JSON.stringify(dev.download_btns);\n  const heightDiffPct = Math.abs(prod.page_height - dev.page_height) / Math.max(prod.page_height, dev.page_height);\n  const imagesDiffPct = Math.abs(prod.rendered_images - dev.rendered_images) / Math.max(prod.rendered_images, dev.rendered_images, 1);\n\n  return {\n    page: path,\n    prod, dev,\n    diff: {\n      headings_match: headingsMatch,\n      downloads_match: downloadsMatch,\n      page_height_diff_pct: Math.round(heightDiffPct * 100),\n      rendered_images_diff_pct: Math.round(imagesDiffPct * 100),\n      sections_diff: prod.elementor_sections - dev.elementor_sections,\n    },\n  };\n}\n```\n\n### Apresentar matriz de paridade\n\n```\n| Página              | PROD height | DEV height | Δ% | PROD H | DEV H | H match | PROD btns | DEV btns | Btns match | Status |\n|---------------------|------------:|-----------:|----|-------:|------:|---------|----------:|---------:|------------|--------|\n| /agenda-integradora |    8420     |    8520    | 1% |    7   |   7   | ✅      |     7     |    7     | ✅         | ✅     |\n```\n\n## Fase 8 — Warm-up de cache do menu (prod e green)\n\nDescobre as páginas do menu principal scrappeando a home, faz 2 visitas em sequência (1ª aquece, 2ª mede), e valida que cada item está sendo servido rápido a partir do cache.\n\n### Snippet — Warm-up do menu (rodar 1x para PROD, 1x para GREEN)\n\n```js\nasync (page) => {\n  const ctx = page.context();\n  const isGreen = HEADER_VAL && HEADER_VAL['X-Test-Green'] === 'true';\n  await ctx.setExtraHTTPHeaders(HEADER_VAL || {});\n  await ctx.clearCookies();\n\n  // 1) Descobrir itens do menu na home\n  await page.goto('https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br/?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 });\n  const menuUrls = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const origin = location.origin;\n    // Cobrir Elementor nav-menu, header padrão WordPress, e <nav> genérico no header\n    const sels = [\n      'header nav a[href]',\n      '.elementor-nav-menu a[href]',\n      '#site-navigation a[href]',\n      '.main-navigation a[href]',\n      'nav.elementor-nav-menu--main a[href]',","numLines":100,"startLine":260,"totalLines":451}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"f39565db-840a-4d76-bcad-92ffdf45e513","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
