{"parentUuid":"58c49318-94c5-4788-835c-e911a51dc6af","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01CvjbJw6ZbRkFVAaTFFWyjr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01G9u6xq8WNRoqNTVJCHjaq7","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2\necho \"=== Diff dos arquivos extras (rapido check) ===\"\nfor f in ec2-deploy/post-deploy/02-php.sh ec2-deploy/post-deploy/03-nginx-sites.sh ec2-deploy/post-deploy/d1-php-fpm-tuning.sh; do\n  echo \"--- $f ---\"\n  git diff --stat \"$f\" | tail -2\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== CHANGELOG.md preview ===\"\ngit diff ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md | head -30","description":"Check extra modified files"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6266,"cache_read_input_tokens":666950,"output_tokens":407,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6266,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":407,"cache_read_input_tokens":666950,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6266,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6266},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CacsnfR38dPmDnF7KheJm","type":"assistant","uuid":"f7e66ccc-bf0e-4486-926a-a02fe3e920c7","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:30:03.323Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"f7e66ccc-bf0e-4486-926a-a02fe3e920c7","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"64bea18c-a7d1-4936-a480-de15c47fa18a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01G9u6xq8WNRoqNTVJCHjaq7","type":"tool_result","content":"=== Diff dos arquivos extras (rapido check) ===\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/02-php.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/02-php.sh | 86 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--\n 1 file changed, 82 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/03-nginx-sites.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/03-nginx-sites.sh | 8 ++++++--\n 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/d1-php-fpm-tuning.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/d1-php-fpm-tuning.sh | 88 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++--\n 1 file changed, 83 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)\n\n=== CHANGELOG.md preview ===\ndiff --git a/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md b/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\nindex 738a39eeb..532da7c0d 100644\n--- a/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\n+++ b/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\n@@ -7,6 +7,97 @@ and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0\n \n ---\n \n+## [1.6.3] - 2026-05-02\n+\n+> **Nota de reconciliacao (Auditor C2.1):** esta versao consolida DUAS\n+> mudancas que foram implementadas em paralelo no ciclo 2 sobre `phase7-cutover.sh`:\n+> (a) novo step 1e (Impl C2.1) e (b) validacao regex dos prefixos de uploads\n+> em `resolve_cf_oac_swap_auto()` (Impl C2.3, originalmente bumpada como 1.6.2).\n+> Ambas coexistem no arquivo final; 1.6.2 ficou como bump intermediario logico,\n+> e 1.6.3 e o estado publicado. Veja entries dedicadas abaixo.\n+\n+### Added\n+\n+- `phase7-cutover.sh` (1.6.2 -> 1.6.3): novo step **1e** — `aws s3 sync` via SSH\n+  do prefixo de prod (`s3://...prd-sa/assets/uploads/`) para o filesystem local\n+  da green (`/var/www/${FQDN}/wp-content/uploads/`). Roda apos o swap S3\n+  (step 1d) e antes do register no prod-tg (step 2). Mesmo gate dos demais\n+  steps CF-OAC (`CF_OAC_SWAP=true`).\n+  - Filtro: `--include='*.svg' --include='*.png' --include='*.jpg' --include='*.jpeg' --include='*.webp' --include='*.gif'` — nao toca CSS de cache do Elementor.\n+  - Idempotente: `--size-only` nao re-baixa; sem `--delete` (nao destrutivo).\n+  - `chown www-data:www-data` pos-sync para garantir leitura por PHP-FPM.\n+  - Falha graciosa: warning + return 0 (nao aborta cutover).\n+  - State: `phases.phase7_cutover.details.step_1e_completed_at` +\n+    `cutover.uploads_fs_sync_count`.\nShell cwd was reset to /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"5a8a67ef-8c96-437b-8424-d2142ae2eef4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:30:03.810Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"=== Diff dos arquivos extras (rapido check) ===\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/02-php.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/02-php.sh | 86 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--\n 1 file changed, 82 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/03-nginx-sites.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/03-nginx-sites.sh | 8 ++++++--\n 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)\n--- ec2-deploy/post-deploy/d1-php-fpm-tuning.sh ---\n ec2-deploy/post-deploy/d1-php-fpm-tuning.sh | 88 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++--\n 1 file changed, 83 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)\n\n=== CHANGELOG.md preview ===\ndiff --git a/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md b/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\nindex 738a39eeb..532da7c0d 100644\n--- a/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\n+++ b/ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/CHANGELOG.md\n@@ -7,6 +7,97 @@ and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0\n \n ---\n \n+## [1.6.3] - 2026-05-02\n+\n+> **Nota de reconciliacao (Auditor C2.1):** esta versao consolida DUAS\n+> mudancas que foram implementadas em paralelo no ciclo 2 sobre `phase7-cutover.sh`:\n+> (a) novo step 1e (Impl C2.1) e (b) validacao regex dos prefixos de uploads\n+> em `resolve_cf_oac_swap_auto()` (Impl C2.3, originalmente bumpada como 1.6.2).\n+> Ambas coexistem no arquivo final; 1.6.2 ficou como bump intermediario logico,\n+> e 1.6.3 e o estado publicado. Veja entries dedicadas abaixo.\n+\n+### Added\n+\n+- `phase7-cutover.sh` (1.6.2 -> 1.6.3): novo step **1e** — `aws s3 sync` via SSH\n+  do prefixo de prod (`s3://...prd-sa/assets/uploads/`) para o filesystem local\n+  da green (`/var/www/${FQDN}/wp-content/uploads/`). Roda apos o swap S3\n+  (step 1d) e antes do register no prod-tg (step 2). Mesmo gate dos demais\n+  steps CF-OAC (`CF_OAC_SWAP=true`).\n+  - Filtro: `--include='*.svg' --include='*.png' --include='*.jpg' --include='*.jpeg' --include='*.webp' --include='*.gif'` — nao toca CSS de cache do Elementor.\n+  - Idempotente: `--size-only` nao re-baixa; sem `--delete` (nao destrutivo).\n+  - `chown www-data:www-data` pos-sync para garantir leitura por PHP-FPM.\n+  - Falha graciosa: warning + return 0 (nao aborta cutover).\n+  - State: `phases.phase7_cutover.details.step_1e_completed_at` +\n+    `cutover.uploads_fs_sync_count`.","stderr":"\nShell cwd was reset to /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"f7e66ccc-bf0e-4486-926a-a02fe3e920c7","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
