{"parentUuid":"ea2e468b-1581-433c-82d9-7cc8d8f63d1e","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Jk48rB4HiMo2wyEvEGsQHM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GLLNxvX3TXB6utMxCNe9Pk","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2\n\necho \"=== Commit 1: 4 scripts blue-green com state_init fix ===\"\ngit add ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/phase4-create-test-rule.sh \\\n        ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/bg-rollback.sh \\\n        ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/phase3-share-and-import.sh \\\n        ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/phase7-cutover.sh \\\n        ec2-deploy/blue-green-automation/phase8-postcutover.sh\ngit commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfix(blue-green): adiciona state_init em 5 scripts (bg-rollback CRITICO)\n\nBug: scripts faziam state_get/state_set/state_phase_* sem ter chamado\nstate_init(), que e obrigatorio para popular _STATE_HELPER_PROJECT.\nstate-helper.sh aborta com \"_STATE_HELPER_PROJECT vazio\" — silenciosamente\nem scripts com stubs no-op locais (perde-se persistencia de state).\n\nCorreção uniforme em main() de cada script, padrão phase1/phase7:\n\n  local script_dir\n  script_dir=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\")\" && pwd)\"\n  local site_dir=\"${script_dir}/../../docker-dev/sites/${PROJECT}\"\n  state_init \"${PROJECT}\" \"${site_dir}\" || true\n\nVersionamento:\n- bg-rollback.sh   1.1.0 → 1.2.0 (CRITICO — rollback estava inutilizavel)\n- phase3-share-and-import.sh 1.2.0 → 1.2.1\n- phase4-create-test-rule.sh 1.1.1 → 1.2.0\n- phase7-cutover.sh 1.6.0 → 1.6.3 (correção comentário linha 1308 v1.4.1+ → v1.5.0+)\n- phase8-postcutover.sh 1.1.1 → 1.1.2\n\nValidação: --help e --dry-run passam sem erro state_init em todos.\n\nDescoberto via auditoria com 5 agentes paralelos (Auditor B+).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit 1: state_init fixes"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1695,"cache_read_input_tokens":673216,"output_tokens":992,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1695,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":992,"cache_read_input_tokens":673216,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1695,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1695},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CacsoPYq9Mi6xUTmpSFu8","type":"assistant","uuid":"d4efcb4b-ca6b-429a-b89e-9d2e72e977b4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:30:22.340Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
